title: Vibe Code a $1M Mobile App in MINUTES (For Beginners)
description:
Build Mobile Apps with Rork: https://rork.com/?ref=brock

In this video I build a mobile app using Rork AI. Unlike Bolt and Lovable, Rork specializes exclusively in mobile apps, making it incredibly powerful yet simple to use. Watch as I demonstrate how you can build professional apps without writing a single line of code!

0:00 - Intro 
0:40 - Why Rork?
1:05 - App idea and features
3:30 - First initial prompt
6:15 - Testing the initial UI and functionality of our app 
7:00 - Adding functionality to the app
10:15 - Github and Cursor integrations 
11:00 - Adding Perplexity API to pull real travel recommendations
13:30 - Testing the app
16:20 - Publishing our app
17:25 - Pricing
